init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: “We will not rest until he is returned to us.”

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The crew ended up going to the alien’s planet and eventually found the one holding Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The crew returned Matt Damon to Earth and the citizens rejoiced in his return.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He then became the President of all Presidents.
